  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Deactivating the Update for External Transactions</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loiod708da531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Deactivating the Update for External Transactions </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> If you do not want to update limits for external transactions, you need to deactivate the external transaction.\n</p>\n<aside class=\"note caution\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Caution</strong></div>\n<p class=\"p\"> This function cannot be used for transactions that have already been saved in the data pool, or for those that have already been updated in end-of-day processing. You can still deactivate a transaction if it has been saved in the data pool but its limit utilization has not yet been updated by end-of-day processing.\n</p></aside>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Procedure\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Procedure</h2>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"></span><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"></span><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"></span> Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tools</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Single Transaction Check</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Deactivate External Transaction</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>\n</p><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> The system displays the screen Single Transaction Check: Deactivate External Transaction</span><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> .</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"></span><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Enter the required data.</span>\n</p><aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n1t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n1t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Choose</span><img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio863adf53e957444de10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Check</span><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> to check that your entries are consistent.</span>\n</p></aside></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loiof6bbdf53e957444de10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Deactivate Trans.</span> , to exclude the transaction from limit updating.\n</p></li></ol>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Result\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Result</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> Under <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Result of Deactivation</span> , the system displays the status of the transaction. Choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio2d52e0530920444de10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Display Log</span> to view the log of the deactivation process.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}